{"tid":1875171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想做標題黨, 但係黃色經濟圈正處危急存亡之秋, 入黎就知我非危言聳聽","createTime":"2020-02-11T15:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T11:10:33.000Z","uid":196536,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"f41e7f604a2106e749a67abca07a7255e5716614","tid":1875171,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:14:12.000Z","msg":"係武漢肺炎爆鑊之前, 黃色經濟圈一直禁住班藍店同垃圾正苦黎打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 勁到屈婦人鳩痕華正苦大陸D廢西報連擊幾十篇文都搞唔掂.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但肺炎殺到, 正當大家大安旨意諗住藍店收皮指日可待, 有冇諗過今次其實反而係<strong>比班藍店茍延殘喘, 黃店先至大難臨頭</strong>?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我而家講下點解.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次肺炎其實香港人大多防疫意識都唔差, 手衛生戴口罩都有做, 同埋最緊要係<span style=\"color: purple;\">減少外出</span>.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過要有呢個意識, 講緊係對生活上習慣上既轉變, 而呢個轉變大家都知一D都唔細.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁對於一D唔鍾意改變, 依然故我既人,其實佢地都係咁樣過日子, 冇錯, 我就係講緊班藍屍.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我屋企附近有間深藍茶記, 去到今日基本上同爆肺炎之前係完全冇分別, 入面冇人戴口罩, 口水橫飛成班廢老. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁大家應該知我想講咩-當<ins>黃絲有意識地減少出街次數, 黃店生意將無可避免受影響</ins>; 但對於<ins>得番藍屍會幫襯既藍店, 肺炎所帶來既衝擊睇黎冇想像中咁大</ins>!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外仲要講多個例子就係<em>藍店大多根底深基業厚, 冇想像咁易收皮; 而黃店大多係新餐廳或由後生仔創立多, 抗逆能力相對遜色</em>..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲覺得我9up? 我最近去過幾次黃店, 午飯晚飯時間, 入到去係一個人都冇.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>係一個人都冇!!食飯時間呀大佬!!!</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我本來一個禮拜只揀兩至三日食黃店, 而家我決定<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">日日食</span></strong>, 因為情況已經非常嚴峻.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位, 抗疫緊要, 但抗爭同樣重要啊. 生活除左口罩漂白水, 仲有手足啊.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n少出街唔緊要, 出親街都盡量幫襯黃店, 頂埋呢關就應該真係打得殘班仆街藍店架啦.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加油啦香港人. 手足要齊上齊落架知唔知.</span></div><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e9aaa5c51400e9f618fdeea60ac0b74e879c38","tid":1875171,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:15:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abf1eeef6e99447f2343d28cd3c455ef863e7535","tid":1875171,"uid":29381,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:16:38.000Z","msg":"lunch去黃店買外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660f83c5be16f0e039dd264b2b88d58fbf1341e3","tid":1875171,"uid":258808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:17:44.000Z","msg":"不嬲都應該日日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90bda441742dcfd2b94599835edfa3d59d4f82a","tid":1875171,"uid":6667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:20:18.000Z","msg":"借位一用 thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n低成本自製面罩抗疫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n。香港人自救，對抗病菌。 「帽」事既！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1875136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1875136</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"32fb6686ff997e5e40f09b1e2eb35a1544fec4e7","tid":1875171,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:20:43.000Z","