gmoji\" /><br />\n另外仲要講多個例子就係<em>藍店大多根底深基業厚, 冇想像咁易收皮; 而黃店大多係新餐廳或由後生仔創立多, 抗逆能力相對遜色</em>..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲覺得我9up? 我最近去過幾次黃店, 午飯晚飯時間, 入到去係一個人都冇.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>係一個人都冇!!食飯時間呀大佬!!!</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我本來一個禮拜只揀兩至三日食黃店, 而家我決定<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">日日食</span></strong>, 因為情況已經非常嚴峻.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位, 抗疫緊要, 但抗爭同樣重要啊. 生活除左口罩漂白水, 仲有手足啊.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n少出街唔緊要, 出親街都盡量幫襯黃店, 頂埋呢關就應該真係打得殘班仆街藍店架啦.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加油啦香港人. 手足要齊上齊落架知唔知.</span></div><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"巴打一定係未聽過 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">打邊爐打到冚家剷</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116420a6fdc2f1f7e35d351da3b6f08db9b22b34","tid":1875171,"uid":271431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:07:31.000Z","msg":"今日先食完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日再食"},{"pid":"a969a477508ed27b5f2823903d0214d942a293f4","tid":1875171,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T16:07:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d00eccab4359d36e629b036ce2eb6424ff81639","tid":1875171,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy